To open the Find / Replace in Files dialog do one of the following:

go to 
            Find
            Find / Replace in Files... 
          ;

click the  Find /
            Replace in Files toolbar button;

go to the contextual menu of the DITA Maps Manager view;

go to the contextual menu of the Project view;

go to the contextual menu of the Data Source Explorer view for
          Documentum xDb (X-Hive/DB), eXist and WebDAV connections. This action is available for
          Documentum (CMS), but lacks the replace feature.
